;------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	;?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?
	; Virtual Peripheral Guidelines Tip:
	; 	The sample rate of this section of code is the isr rate / 4, because it is jumped
	;	to in every 4th entry in the VP Multitaskers table.  To increase the
